00:04:25.900 --> 00:04:30.200
So, supply going down will
shift to the left and up.

00:04:30.200 --> 00:04:32.071
Once again, one way to think about it

00:04:32.071 --> 00:04:36.027
at a given price you would
be willing to supply less,

00:04:36.027 --> 00:04:39.048
